title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update- Sim Update IX - What to expect?
description:
Beta testing of Sim Update 9 has already started a few weeks back and it is almost time for the release of Sim Update 9 which is currently scheduled to be available on the 26th of April. In parallel to the Sim Update a new Famous Flyer will be available which brings the number of Famous Flyers to 2. In this video we will look at what to expect from this Sim Update including the new spotlight event which is part of the Sim Update.
